attachments.title: How to Be a Good Manager
attachments.text: We're working on an article for <http://Uptickapp.com|Uptickapp.com> about how to be a great manager. We're looking for advice from a range of people — experienced managers, new managers, and even employees who want to share what makes a manager "good" in their eyes. We're particularly interested in advice that focuses on building better teams. All quotes used in the article will be attributed with a backlink to your site. Thank you for sharing your advice!

Hey folks! I'm working on an article around *retail marketing for ecommerce marketplaces.* I'm looking for a few *B2B marketers* to do an email or phone interview with (and add a link back to your site, of course).

I'm specifically looking for marketers who have helped launched a marketplace or whose solution has helped launch a marketplace. Huge plus points if you helped a brick & mortar retailer transition to ecommerce.

We've featured VPs and C-suites from places like Shopify Plus, commercetools, and Lightspeed in previous articles, so you'll be in good ecommerce company.

If you or someone you know fits the bill, please comment on this message or send me a DM! :heart:
